                                text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;>How do new medicines originate? Meet the team behind early development of AbbVie’s immunology treatments.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
